---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Comunidades
description: Diretório aberto de comunidades de tecnologia com leitura direta e filtro simples.
bodyClass: page-communities
pageScripts:
  - /assets/js/list-filters.js
---
{% set allCommunities = collections.communitiesSorted %}
{% set stateOptions = allCommunities | uniqueStates %}

<section class="utility-intro utility-intro--soft">
  <div class="container utility-intro__inner" data-reveal>
    <p class="eyebrow">Diretório</p>
    <h1>Encontre comunidades tech por estado, cidade ou tema.</h1>
    <p>
      Busque por nome, filtre por estado e abra os links principais com uma leitura direta.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="listing-shell" data-list-root>
  <div class="container listing-shell__toolbar" data-reveal>
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Índice</p>
      <h2><span data-results-count>{{ allCommunities.length }}</span> comunidades</h2>
    </div>
    <button class="filter-toggle" type="button" data-filter-toggle aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="community-filters">
      Filtrar
    </button>
  </div>

  <div class="filter-backdrop" data-filter-backdrop hidden></div>

  <div class="container listing-shell__layout">
    <aside class="filter-panel" id="community-filters" data-filter-panel>
      <div class="filter-panel__header">
        <h3>Filtros</h3>
        <button class="filter-panel__close" type="button" data-filter-close>Fechar</button>
      </div>

      <form class="filter-form" aria-label="Filtros de comunidades" data-filter-form>
        <label>
          <span>Buscar</span>
          <input type="search" placeholder="Nome, cidade, tag..." data-filter-search>
        </label>
        <label>
          <span>Estado</span>
          <select data-filter-key="state">
            <option value="">Todos</option>
            {% for state in stateOptions %}
              <option value="{{ state }}">{{ state | stateName }}</option>
            {% endfor %}
          </select>
        </label>
        <div class="filter-actions">
          <button class="button button--primary" type="submit">Aplicar filtros</button>
          <button class="button button--ghost" type="button" data-filter-reset>Limpar</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </aside>

    <div class="listing-shell__content">
      <section class="listing-block" data-filter-section>
        <div class="listing-list">
          {% for community in allCommunities %}
            {% include "partials/community-card.njk" %}
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
        <p class="empty-inline" data-section-empty hidden>Nenhuma comunidade combina com os filtros.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
